{"id": "1429816360015364228", "channel_id": "1429816360015364228", "type": 0, "author_id": "891201145991753729", "author_name": "faithzero.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Hi, so I read the patch notes and Casiah's enlightenment 3 has now a discard effect. My question is does Casiah now trigger other awakeners discard effect or just her cards? When I try to use Poof to discard my cards I can't seem to see my tentacle damage increasing. Am I missing something?? The team I run with is Corpo, Aurita, Tulu, Casiah", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T12:59:44.931000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429816360015364228", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Casiah New E3", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1429830481406595336", "channel_id": "1429816360015364228", "type": 0, "author_id": "267888098732539914", "author_name": "2ndselna", "author_bot": false, "content": "From the patch notes, her reshuffle hand triggers aftershock should be in soulforge aptitude (arc 2 talent). If you havent unlocked it or you are using her in arc 1 ruleset stages, it will not trigger.", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:55:51.733000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "❤️", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429816360015364228", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Casiah New E3", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1400747489132412979"]}
{"id": "1429788515998109797", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "104682949340848128", "author_name": "aleksanteri", "author_bot": false, "content": "How does the timeless call, Chronos Mandate banner work? I selected an Awakener last patch, now my banner still has 13 days to go. Do I get to choose again when it ends, or do I have to wait some time for the next patch or something?\n\nAlso, is there a decent team to beat the story with I can make out of these guys? I feel like im kind of missing a bunch of DPS as well, so im wondering what should I choose on the Chronos Mandate banner if/when I can choose again, probably Genesis Helot right? Also wondering if Pulling on standard banner to try and get Jenkins is a good idea.", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T11:09:06.400000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1429788516321333329", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 925720, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1429788515998109797/1429788516321333329/image.png?ex=69ccfcd2&is=69cbab52&hm=1ce0320f50ef5a65837e78de2a7f24b888b1d793733ae6ac3d10eed4653b04eb&"}, {"id": "1429788516992159885", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 681389, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1429788515998109797/1429788516992159885/image.png?ex=69ccfcd2&is=69cbab52&hm=62cc54ebee2e0da08f424c01641a2993a6ac1ecaa802ac31271de3b9ad9d6bad&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429788634713690162", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 4, "author_id": "104682949340848128", "author_name": "aleksanteri", "author_bot": false, "content": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T11:09:34.704000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429823993636196352", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "Timeless Call / Chronos Mandate banner lets you choose a limited SSR character from arc 1 (faded legacy) to be the rate up character", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:30:04.928000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:52:49.844000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429824134921060414", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "That chosen SSR character and its signature SSR WoD (wheel of destiny) \nwill be the target character or wheel", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:30:38.613000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:54:30.616000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429828181489356840", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "The hard pity for this banner is 60 pulls for both the chosen character or signature wheel unlike normal limited/event banners wherein it's 90 pulls (character) and 60 pulls (wheel)", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:46:43.390000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:47:18.258000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429829155687628911", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "There is also another guarantee mechanic for this banner. If you get both the same rate up in a row, the third time you are quaranteed the other rate up.", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:50:35.657000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429831367147126875", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "For example, let's say you chose Tawil as rate up\nIf you get Tawil twice in a row, the third time you'll get her WoD \"Wheel Unseen\"\nIf you get Wheel Unseen twice in a row instead, you'll get Tawil on the third time", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T13:59:22.910000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-20T14:02:37.914000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429832085429813412", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "You could get the other rate up immediately if your lucky\nTawil then Wheel Unseen or\nWheel Unseen then Tawil", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T14:02:14.162000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429833852762718270", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "The banner is good if you're aiming to get both the character and signature WoD", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T14:09:15.527000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429836153988714606", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "The banner gets removed when it ends until the next time the devs decide to rerun it", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T14:18:24.182000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-10-20T14:18:33.833000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
{"id": "1429836941263769660", "channel_id": "1429788515998109797", "type": 0, "author_id": "596922317142228992", "author_name": "juuki0811", "author_bot": false, "content": "When they do, the rate up will reset allowing you to chose again", "timestamp": "2025-10-20T14:21:31.883000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1429788515998109797", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Chronos Mandate banner & Some teambuilding help.", "forum_channel_id": "1356200968311803956", "thread_tags": ["1359076287846682704", "1400747088995811358"]}
